      "span_text": "The relative importance values are determined with Saaty's 1-9 scale, where a score of 1 represents equal importance between the two elements and a score of 9 indicates the extreme importance of one element (row cluster in the matrix) compared to the other one (column cluster in the matrix) [CITATION_1] ."
